snippet.title: Dig or Die v1.0 trailer
snippet.description:
New in Dig or Die v1.0, to be released on July 10th:
- 3 new game modes : Under the Sea, Sky World, and Base Defense
- Hazardous Environment option to get random events like Meteor Shower, Rain Flood, Volcano Eruption, Earthquake, Sharkstorm...
- Creative mode
- 9 new musics
